<B>__{title sequence}
<A>__{the faces of several young children are presented in closeup, as they walk toward us across a ploughed field. on the sound track, the haunting sounds of a gregorian funeral chant. the camera pans up to the faces of older brothers and sisters, then to parents and grandparents. these are not familiar faces, but faces from another age, strong and open. all are dressed in the distinctive clothing of the amish.}
